    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s in really solid condition and still has plenty of life left in it! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs great, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics, so it's ready to go whenever you are. Come take a look\u2014I'd love for it to go to a good home!",
