      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this expertly maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and value. This unit has been curated for the discerning driver who demands mechanical consistency and a refined interior environment. Demonstrating a clear history of diligent upkeep, the vehicle exhibits robust handling and a clean, professional aesthetic profile. It stands as a testament to enduring engineering, providing a reliable and prestigious driving experience for its next owner.",
