    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I'm parting ways with my car, and it has been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved and looked after. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways alike. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come on by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels behind the wheel!",
