    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This example delivers exceptional throttle response through its six individual throttle bodies and remains structurally robust following a proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile gear selection, sending power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential lock. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle, the suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and dampers. A compelling, turn-key choice for those demanding a pure, analog driving experience without the premium of a garage queen.",
